---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro'; 
const rawBase = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const base = rawBase.endsWith('/') ? rawBase : `${rawBase}/`;
---

<style>
h1 {text-align: center; font-size: 60px}
p {text-align: center;}
div {text-align: center;}
h2 {text-align: center;}
</style>

<Layout title="home">

  <section class="page-selection">
    <h1><b><br>SALEEM<br>MOHAMMED<br>ALI</b></h1>
    <p style="font-size: 24px"><b>UNDERGRADUATE MECHANICAL ENGINEERING PORTFOLIO<br>
      
    <div class="grid-container2">
      <div class="column">
        <a href={`${base}projects/`} class="card">
          <h2>PROJECTS</h2>
        </a>

      </div>
      <div class="column">
        <a href={`${base}resume/`} class="card">
          <h2>RESUME</h2>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
      
    <br><br><br><br><br></b></p>
  </section>

<!--   <img src="/images/takumi.jpg" alt="takumis ae86" width="300" /> -->

  <section class="home-section; custom-spacing;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 40px; text-align: left"><b>ME</b></h2>
    <p style="text-align: left;"> 
      
      Who am I? you ask. I am a mechanical engineering undergrad at the University of Waterloo. I've always been completely fascinated by how things work, so much so, you can say I eat, sleep, and breathe all things mechanical. I'm a very hands-on,
       crafty person who enjoys being involved in the entire product lifecycle: starting from sketching out a new concept, to testing it to its limits, and iterating until it's the closest thing to perfect. My biggest passion is the automotive industry; 
       I think cars are one of the greatest inventions out there. My ultimate dream? To engineer a part, 
      put it through its paces, and one day own the car it goes into, just so I can proudly say, 'I helped make this drive.' My career goal is simple; to build a career out of doing exactly what I love.      <br><br><br><br>
    </p>

    <p style="text-align: center; border: 3px solid var(--link-color); padding: 0px; max-width: 350px; margin: auto; font-size: 0px;">
        <img src={`${base}images/machining-edit.jpg`} alt="me-machining" width="350px"/>
    </p>
    <br><br>
  </section>

  <section>

    <div class="grid-container3">
        <div class="column">
            <h3 style="font-size: 26px">interests</h3>
            <p style="text-align: left; margin-left: 3.5rem;">
              ✇ cars and aircrafts<br>
              🛠 mechanical design<br>
              ⚡︎ electronic systems<br>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
            <h3 style="font-size: 26px">strengths</h3>
             <p style="text-align: left; margin-left: 4.5rem;">
              ⏣ machining :)<br>
              ☆ quick learner<br>
              ☆ problem solver<br>
              <br>
             </p>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
            <h3 style="font-size: 26px">weaknesses</h3>
              <p style="text-align: left; margin-left: 3.5rem;">
              ⏣ machining :(<br>
              ☆ prefer hands on work<br>
              ☆ over meticulous<br>
              </p>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    <section>
    <h2 style="font-size: 40px;"><b>LET'S CONNECT</b></h2>
    <div class="contact-container">
      <div class="contact-info-group">
        <div class="contact-links">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/s7mohamm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span><img src={`${base}icons/linkedIn-48px.png`} alt="linkedin-icon" width="36px"/></span> <b>LinkedIn</b>
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/s7mo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span><img src={`${base}icons/github-48px.png`} alt="github-icon" width="36px"/></span> <b>GitHub</b>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-email">
          <b>Email: </b><a href="mailto:s7mohamm@uwaterloo.ca"> <b>s7mohamm@uwaterloo.ca</b></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-form-group">
        <form class="contact-form" name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" action="https://getform.io/f/apjzjpga">
          <label for="user-email">Your Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="user-email" name="email" required />
          <label for="user-message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="user-message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
          <button type="submit"><b>Send</b></button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <br><br><br>
</Layout>



